Sentence: Among the commercially available superconductors, magnesium diboride (MgB2) with critical temperature (Tc) of 39 K has good potential to employ in rotating machines .

An in situ processed S-glass-insulated 36-filament MgB2 wire was wound on the former in two layers with The coil was evaluated for critical temperature and transport critical current in the SN2 environment at different temperatures up to 31.3 K in self-field.
